OL,3,CPart of major Welsh road to close for
OL,4,Cthree months to repair fire damage
OL,6,FPart of a major Welsh road is to close
OL,7,Ffor three months as work gets underway
OL,8,Fto repair fire damage to a mountain.
OL,10,FMotorists and cyclists have been
OL,11,Fwarned that there will be disruption
OL,12,Fon part of the A4061 Rhigos Mountain
OL,13,FRoad as "complex engineering works"
OL,14,Ftake place to fix damage to the
OL,15,Fmountain caused by a major fire.
OL,17,FThe road will close from Monday, July
OL,18,F22 as engineers attempt to make the
OL,19,Fmountain safe after damage caused to
OL,20,Fthe protective netting on the slopes
OL,21,Fby a 2022 grass fire.
