OL,6,FA full road closure is being put in
OL,7,Fplace in order to rectify the damage.
OL,8,FThe repair scheme is currently
OL,9,Fscheduled to conclude by the end of
OL,10,FOctober 2024.
OL,12,FThe work area is located at the
OL,13,Fsouthern end of the A4061 Rhigos
OL,14,FMountain Road, over a length of
OL,15,Fapproximately 375-metres.
